com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class SessionParties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.SessionParties

  • public class SessionParties
extends Object
    Encapsulates the session's party and counterparty id components which provide the defaults when values are not already set in a message. These can be set out of order via the API so a Party isn't appropriate.

      • getConnectionPoint

        public IConnectionPoint getConnectionPoint()
        Create connection point defined by the IParty with whom we are communicating, the IParty by which we are known to them, and the ID of the application to which this session belongs.

        If either the external party or our party are null (i.e. in the case of an anonymous session) a "null party" new Party(null, null, null) is used to substitute it and create the connection point.

        Returns:
        the IConnectionPoint for this session. Never null.
